This paper deals with reinforcement learning and policy gradient methods, which are commonly studied in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of entropy bonus to encourage exploration, which is a common technique in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper applies the proposed algorithms to multi-agent problems, which fall under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also involves optimization and control, which are studied in the categories of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
